Twitter API:
https://dev.twitter.com/rest/reference/get/search/tweets

Tutorial:
http://socialmedia-class.org/twittertutorial.html

Twitter Python Library
https://pypi.python.org/pypi/twitter

Install Twitter Python Library
$ cd twitter-1.17.1
$ python setup.py --help
$ python setup.py build
$ python setup.py install


Aditional Filters

https://dev.twitter.com/streaming/overview/request-parameters


Run
python twitter_streaming.py


For the output  saved it in a txt file
python twitter_streaming.py > twitter_stream_1000tweets.txt

---
Run Timeline

python twitter-user-timeline.py

For the output  saved it in a txt file
python twitter-user-timeline.py  > twitter_user_timeline.txt